summary.span: Fornece um ouvinte que roteia todas as saídas de rastreamento e depuração para a infraestrutura de IIS 7.0.

span.span: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.

remarks.format: ## Remarks O classe conecta o mecanismo de rastreamento do [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] para [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].The class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]. Essa classe de escuta permite que os desenvolvedores que criam [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] aplicativos e que implementam a e interfaces para elevar o nível de página, nível de módulo ou nível de manipulador de eventos para o [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] durante o rastreamento de infraestrutura está habilitado.This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the and interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled. > [!NOTE] > Essa classe de ouvinte não roteia [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] eventos às classes do ASP.NET.This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes. Isso inclui o classe e classes que implementam o ou interface.This includes the class and classes that implement the or interface. é apresentado na [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. Para saber mais, confira [Versões e dependências](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
